+# Mod 00 — joy App
+
+## What
+Personal build of Happy with a separate app identifier and mobile icon.
+
+## Changes
+- `src-tauri/tauri.joy.conf.json` — overrides productName, identifier (`com.farazyashar.joy`), and icon to use `icon-joy.icns`
+- `src-tauri/icons/icon-joy.icns` — generated from `sources/assets/images/icon.png` (the 1024×1024 mobile icon) via `iconutil`
+- `package.json` — adds `tauri:joy` (dev) and `tauri:build:joy` (release) scripts
+
+## Why Not Upstream
+No conflicts expected — all new files. `package.json` scripts section may drift if upstream adds new tauri scripts nearby.
diff --git a/packages/happy-app/package.json b/packages/happy-app/package.json
index 37eab58a0..38c88465e 100644
--- a/packages/happy-app/package.json
+++ b/packages/happy-app/package.json
@@ -38,7 +38,9 @@
     "tauri:dev": "tauri dev --config src-tauri/tauri.dev.conf.json",
     "tauri:build:dev": "tauri build --config src-tauri/tauri.dev.conf.json",
     "tauri:build:preview": "tauri build --config src-tauri/tauri.preview.conf.json",
-    "tauri:build:production": "tauri build"
+    "tauri:build:production": "tauri build",
+    "tauri:joy": "tauri dev --config src-tauri/tauri.joy.conf.json",
+    "tauri:build:joy": "tauri build --config src-tauri/tauri.joy.conf.json"
   },
   "jest": {
     "preset": "jest-expo"
